      "text": [
        "٤٣٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): اذْكُرُوا انْقِطَاعَ الَّلذَّاتِ، وَبَقَاءَ التَّبِعَاتِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "433. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Remember that pleasures will pass away while the consequences will stay"
